 | last3 = Clayton | first3 = D. A.
 | title = Elongation of displacement-loop strands in human and mouse mitochondrial DNA is arrested near specific template sequences
 | journal = Proceedings of the National Academy of Sciences of the United States of America
 | volume = 78
 | issue = 10
 | pages = 6116–6120
 | year = 1981
 | pmid = 6273850
 | pmc = 348988
 | doi=10.1073/pnas.78.10.6116
}}</ref>。

D環結構通常出現在線粒體DNA上的主要非編碼區域。這一區域通常稱爲{{Link-en|線粒體DNA控制區域|mtDNA control region|控制區域}}或D環區域。

線粒體DNA可以兩種方式進行複製，這兩種方式在初始階段都會出現D環<ref name=fish>{{Cite journal
